Join us at Alice's on Bayview
​
​
We look forward to serving our favorite classic southern dishes for brunch, lunch and dinner right here in Historic St. Andrews. Enjoy fresh seafood, smoked chicken, steak and much more. Grab a table with a view of St. Andrews Bay and the Marina, or sit at the bar to enjoy casual dining at its best.
​
We hope to see you soon!
​
Alice Masker
